f%20my%20time%20in%20Donbas%2C%20which%20is%20the%20Donetsk%20and%20Luhansk%20Oblast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20with%20the%20Marines%20and%20now%20work%20with%20three%20different%20brigades.%20These%20guys%20are%20like%20my%20family.%20Unfortunately%2C%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20soldiers%20have%20been%20injured.%20Some%20have%20been%20killed.%20And%20that%20has%20been%20very%20difficult.%20But%20we%20stick%20together.%20On%20Thanksgiving%2C%20we%20will%20all%20be%20here%20together%2C%20on%20the%20front.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20with%20just%20doing%20evacuations%2C%20and%20then%20I%20noticed%20that%20the%20soldiers%20didn't%20have%20first%20aid%20kits.%20They%20weren't%20receiving%20a%20lot%20of%20medical%20training.%20So%20then%20I%20started%20to%20do%20both.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20some%20of%20our%20soldiers%20pass%20away%20after%20receiving%20Chinese%20replica%20tourniquets.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-soldiers-need-tourniquets-armored-cars-wounded-troops-2023-10%5C%22%3ETourniquets%20are%20devices%20used%20to%20apply%20pressure%20to%20a%20limb%20or%20extremity%20in%20order%20to%20stop%20the%20flow%20of%20blood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20am%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20them.%20If%20you%20have%20arterial%20bleeding%2C%20you%20can%20die%20in%20three%20minutes%2C%20and%20if%20that%20tourniquet%20breaks%2C%20there's%20no%20chance%20for%20you.%20Statistically%2C%20three%20out%20of%20four%20wounded%20soldiers%20in%20this%20conflict%20can%20die%20from%20hemorrhagic%20blood%20loss.%20So%2C%20high-quality%20tourniquets%20became%20a%20really%20important%20topic%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22undefined%5C%22%20data-cards%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%94Rebekah%20Maciorowski%20(%40bekamaciorowski