cal%20medical%20training%20to%20soldiers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6556456e36d588dc55d196bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22710%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERebekah%20Maciorowski%20addressing%20a%20group%20of%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20during%20tactical%20medical%20training.%3Cp%3E53rd%20Mechanized%20Brigade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20an%20anonymous%20gentleman%20who%20wrote%20a%20check%20for%20%242%2C000%20for%20tactical%20medical%20supplies.%20And%20because%20I'm%20not%20a%20501(c)%20organization%2C%20he%20gave%20it%20to%20this%20other%20organization%20and%20wrote%20them%20a%20handwritten%20letter%20explaining%20these%20are%20for%20medical%20supplies%20for%20Rebekah%20Maciorowski.%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAwesome.%20Here%20is%20where%20you%20can%20use%20this%20money%20directly%20and%20buy%20the%20necessary%20equipment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20no%2C%20we're%20actually%20going%20to%20get%20all%20of%20this%20in%20the%20US.%20We're%20gonna%20wait%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half.%20We're%20gonna%20fly%20it%20over.%20We're%20gonna%20caravan%20it%20to%20you%2C%20and%20we're%20gonna%20make%20a%20big%20social%20media%20post.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombat%20injuries%20can't%20wait%20that%20long.%20There%20are%20new%20casualties%20every%20day.%20I%20told%20them%20we%20needed%20those%20supplies%20yesterday%20and%20that%20we%20were%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20an%20assault.%20They%20refused%20to%20buy%20the%20equipment%20I%20requested%20from%20my%20trusted%20suppliers%2C%20which%20would%20have%20ensured%20the%20arrival%20of%20adequate%20supplies%20in%20a%20timely%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20they%20did%20a%20whole%20%26quot%3BDonbas%20Safari%26quot%3B%20trying%20to%20take%20some%20of%20my%20soldiers%20for%20photo%20ops%2C%20and%20then%20asked%20for%20an%20official%20thank%20you%20letter%20for%20bringing%20this%20all%20to%20me.%20This%20happ