laint%20also%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20used%20other%20derogatory%20terms%20and%20made%20unverified%20allegations%20during%20his%20campaign%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20assembly%20elections%20are%20due%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20use%20of%20such%20language%20is%20%26quot%3Bunbecoming%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20senior%20leader%2C%20the%20complaint%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20notice%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20prohibits%20leaders%20from%20making%20unverified%20allegations%20against%20political%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20speaking%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20accused%20PM%20Modi%20of%20attempting%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20key%20issues%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20comes%20on%20TV%20and%20says%20'Hindu-Muslim'%20and%20sometimes%20goes%20to%20a%20cricket%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20boys%20would%20have%20won%20the%20World%20Cup%20but%20the%20panauti%20(bad%20omen)%20lost%20us%20the%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20then%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20India's%20defeat%20to%20Australia%20at%20the%20World%20Cup%20finals%20on%20Sunday.%20%26quot%3BPM%20means%20Panauti%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20had%20attended%20the%20match%2C%20played%20at%20a%20stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad%20named%20after%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20comment%2C%20complete%20with%20memes%2C%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20furious%20BJP%20demanded%20an%20apology.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20said%20the%20comment%20was%20%26quot%3Bshameful%2C%20condemnable%20and%20disgraceful%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrashekar%20said%20they%20indicated%20%26quot%3Bdesperation%20and%20mental%20instability%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26