E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tried%20to%20better%20myself%20trying%20to%20get%20an%20education%2C%20trying%20to%20get%20somewhere%2C%20but%20apparently%20I%20did%20it%20too%20late%20in%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20criminal%20history%2C%20nothing%20but%20good%20employment%20history%2C%20and%20I%20just%20couldn't%20get%20a%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Fleshren%20has%20just%20over%20%2437%2C000%20in%20student%20debt%20from%20his%20bachelor's%20degree%2C%20according%20to%20documents%20reviewed%20by%20Insider%2C%20and%20while%20he's%20been%20able%20to%20pay%20his%20bill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-repayment-issues-debt-relief-broken-industry-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esince%20monthly%20federal%20student-loan%20payments%20resumed%20in%20October%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said%20he's%20not%20sure%20how%20much%20longer%20he%20can%20afford%20to%20do%20so%20while%20also%20juggling%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20medical%20bills%20for%20his%20wife's%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chris%20Fleshren%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e20ef22cf74a5739b7d22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChris%20Fleshren%20has%20%2437%2C000%20in%20student%20debt.%3Cp%3EChris%20Fleshren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20borrowers%20are%20now%20dealing%20with%20a%20monthly%20bill%20they%20haven't%20paid%20in%20over%20three%20years%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%20pause%20on%20student-loan%20payments.%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Education%20Department%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-best-way-to-pay-student-loan-debt-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimplemented%20a%2012-month%20%26quot%3Bon-ramp%26quot%3B%20period%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20which%20it%20won't%20actively%20report%20any%20missed%20payments%20to%20credit%20agencies%2C%20along%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-borrowers-apply-income-driven-repayment-save-plan-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20intended%20to%20lower%20borrowers'%20monthly%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that%20relief%20isn't%20enough%20for%20some%20borrowers%20as%20they%20struggle%20to%20afford%20basic%20necessities%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20defaulted.%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20stay%20up%20to%20date%20on%20the%20payments.%20But%20I'm%20not%20convinced%20in%20the%20least%20that%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20continue%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Fleshren%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20about%20two%20months%20worth%20of%20bills%2C%20maybe%20three%20months%20worth%20of%20bills%2C%20in%20my%20checking%20account%20and%20we%20have%20no%20savings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20year%20or%20two%20away%20from%20retirement.%20Are%20they%20going%20to%20make%20me%20pay%20a%20fourth%20of%20my%20Social%20Security%20to%20pay%20off%20my%20student%20loans%20when%20I'm%2066%20years%20old%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'There's%20just%20too%20many%20payments'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20process%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-long-will-take-cancel-student-debt-higher-education-act-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrafting%20its%20new%20plan%20for%20student-loan%20forgiveness.%3C%2Fa%3E%20At%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruck%20down%20the%20department's%20first%20attempt%20at%20broad%20debt%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20it's%20using%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Act%20of%201965%20to%20tailor%20a%20new%20relief%20plan%20that%20will%20be%20more%20narrow%20than%20the%20first%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20requires%20the%20department%20to%20undergo%20a%20process%20called%20negotiated%20rulemaking%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20series%20of%20negotiation%20sessions%20and%20period%20of%20public%20comment%20before%20publishing%20the%20final%20rule.%20The%20department%20recently%20asked%20negotiators%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loans-forgiveness-borrowers-prove-hardship-debt-relief-education-department-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20it%20define%20what%20would%20qualify%20as%20%26quot%3Bhardship%26quot%3B%20for%20borrowers%20to%20get%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Fleshren%20hopes%20his%20situation%20meets%20the%20criteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20my%20wife's%20car%2C%20plus%20food%2C%20plus%20utilities%2C%20plus%20the%20mortgage%2C%20plus%20the%20car%20payment%2C%26quot%3B%20Fleshren%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20just%20too%20many%20payments%20and%20if%20I%20don't%20qualify%20for%20hardship%2C%20I%20just%20don't%20know%20what%20I'm%20going%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENegotiators%20floated%20a%20range%20of%20ideas%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20who%20might%20qualify%20for%20hardship%2C%20including%20Pell%20Grant%20recipients%2C%20borrowers%20with%20a%20disability%2C%20or%20those%20dealing%20with%20significant%20childcare%20or%20medical%20expenses.%20The%20negotiating%20committee%20will%20meet%20one%20more%20time%20in%20December%20to%20provide%20input%20on%20Biden's%20next%20attempt%20at%20relief%2C%20and%20Fleshren%20said%20giving%20all%20his%20spare%20time%20to%20caring%20for%20his%20wife%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20keeps%20me%20from%20getting%20another%20job%20to%20help%20pay%20my%20loans%20and%20debts%2C%20should%20be%20factored%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%