rations%20Command%2C%20also%20has%20special-operations%20units%20on%20constant%20standby%20to%20respond%20to%20any%20terrorism%20or%20hostage%20situations%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20DSS%20initiative%20aims%20to%20give%20diplomats%20and%20their%20families%20the%20tools%20to%20survive%20overseas.%20The%20Foreign%20Affairs%20Counter%20Threat%20training%20program%20is%20a%20five-day%20course%20that%20provides%20diplomats%20and%20their%20families%20with%20skills%20to%20enhance%20their%20security%20awareness%20and%20preparedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20relations%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.19fortyfive.com%2F2023%2F10%2Fhistoric-tragedy-the-war-in-ukraine-continues-to-be-a-bloody-stalemate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussia%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20China%20have%20deteriorated%2C%20the%20DSS%20has%20had%20to%20adjust%20its%20activities%20to%20ensure%20it%20can%20protect%20US%20facilities%20in%20those%20countries%20and%20the%20diplomats%20and%20staff%20at%20them%2C%20but%20it's%20dealing%20with%20a%20growing%20set%20of%20threats%20from%20outside%20the%20physical%20realm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EProliferating%20cyber%20threats%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Diplomatic%20Security%20Service%20computer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e187d4ca513d8242d8a22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDSS%20personnel%20worked%20with%20other%20law-enforcement%20agencies%20at%20the%20APEC%20summit%20in%20San%20Francisco%20in%20November%202023.%3Cp%3EDiplomatic%20Security%20Service%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20string%20of%20high-profile%20cyberattacks%20against%20government%20agencies%20and%20private%20businesses%2C%20US%20national-security%20officials%20are%20increasingly%20focused%20on%20cybersecurity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20understands%20that%20the%20State%20Department's%20IT%20netw