ten%20on%20board%20with%20the%20four-day%20workweek%20hype%20and%20given%20up%20working%20on%20Fridays%20because%20%26quot%3Bit's%20just%20pointless%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20British%20tabloid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Ftvandshowbiz%2F24773644%2Fsimon-cowell-works-four-days-week-strict-rules%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20Sun%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECowell%2C%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20talent%20shows%20like%20X%20Factor%20and%20America's%20Got%20Talent%2C%20revealed%20how%20he%20strikes%20a%20work-life%20balance%20alongside%20filming%20as%20a%20judge%20for%20his%20TV%20shows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2064-year-old%20said%20that%20he%20used%20to%20be%20a%20workaholic%20and%20clocked%20in%2020%20hours%20of%20work%20a%20day%20running%20shows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20anyone%20should%20be%20working%20five%20days%20a%20week.%20It's%20just%20pointless%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20The%20Sun.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20work%20on%20Fridays%2C%20because%20you%20don't%20have%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BEat%20dinner%20at%20five%20o'clock.%20Don't%20take%20calls%20after%205.30.%20Don't%20read%20emails%20after%205.30.%20Watch%20a%20happy%20movie.%20And%20stay%20outside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20evidence%20that%20a%20four-day%20workweek%20can%20be%20beneficial.%20A%20six-month%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-day-workweek-successful-trial-evidence-productivity-retention-revenue-2023-1%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etrial%20conducted%20in%202022%20that%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20involved%2033%20companies%20with%20employees%20in%20six%20different%20countries%2C%20found%20that%20the%20companies%20who%20participated%20saw%20increased%20revenue%20and%20better%20wellbeing%20and%20health%20for%20their%20employees%20when%20they%20dropped%20to%20four%20days.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3