izona%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20New%20York%2C%20Florida%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Tennessee%2C%20Virginia%2C%20Missouri%2C%20and%20Illinois.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20holidays%20are%20some%20of%20our%20biggest%20dollar%20amount%20bookings%2C%20so%20it's%20so%20important%20that%20everything%20goes%20smoothly%20and%20that%20guests%20have%20no%20surprises%20when%20they%20check%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luxury%20home%20with%20a%20basketball%20court%2C%20swimming%20pool%2C%20hot%20tub%2C%20and%20patio%20in%20the%20backyard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655cda9222cf74a5739ac5ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222676%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Techvestor%20property%20in%20Arizona.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Austin%20Weinerman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20Florida%2C%20we%20have%20a%205-bedroom%20home%20geared%20towards%20families%20with%20a%20fire%20pit%2C%20a%20pool%2C%20a%20jungle%20gym%2C%20an%20under-the-sea%20themed%20kids%20playroom.%20It%20usually%20rents%20for%20%24400%20to%20%24700%20per%20night%20depending%20if%20it's%20a%20weekday%20or%20weekend.%20For%20Thanksgiving%2C%20it%20will%20book%20for%20%241%2C500%20to%20%241%2C700%20per%20night%20and%20for%20Christmas%20season%20it%20will%20go%20for%20%242%2C000%20to%20%242%2C300.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20reserve%20back%20up%20turkeys%20and%20double%20check%20for%20oven%20racks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20Thanksgiving%2C%20we%20were%20around%2020%20to%2030%20properties%20that%20were%20live%20%E2%80%94%20now%20we're%20at%20105%20to%20110.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20developed%20a%20specific%20holiday%20checklist.%20So%20in%20the%20two%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20Thanksgiving%2C%20we%20send%20someone%20to%20every%20single%20one%20of%20our%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20check%20the%20ovens%2C%20the%20stoves%2C%20how%20many%20dishes%20are%20in%20the%20home%2C%20how%20many%20pieces%20of%20silverware%2C%20surveying%20all%20the%20kitchen%20appliances%20and%20cookware%20to%20make%20sure%20they're%20functional.%20We%20check%20on%20the%20highly-used%20amenities%20like%20the%20hot%20tub%20or%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20each%20of%20our%20markets%2C%20we've%20also%20reached%20out%20ahead%20of%20time%20to%20at%20least%20two%20or%20three%20restaurants.%20We%20essentially%20have%20a%20turkey%20on%20stand%20by.%20We%20can%20spend%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20holiday%20checking%20all%20the%20ovens%2C%20but%20something%20can%20always%20go%20wrong%20the%20day%20of.%20We%20talk%20to%20these%20restaurants%20ahead%20of%20time%20and%20pre-order%20enough%20turkeys%20for%20our%20bookings.%20If%20the%20oven%20stops%20working%20on%20the%20big%20day%2C%20we%20can%20have%20a%20turkey%20for%20guests%20in%20one%20to%20two%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20our%20properties%20are%20booked%20for%20Thanksgiving%2C%20around%20105%20homes%20across%20nine%20states.%20We're%20fully%20stocked%20across%20each%20market%2C%20so%20there%20shouldn't%20be%20a%20scenario%20where%20someone%20goes%20without%20a%20turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20Thanksgiving%2C%20someone%20had%20taken%20out%20oven%20racks%20in%20one%20of%20our%20homes%20and%20our%20cleaners%20didn't%20catch%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20have%20this%20lineup%20of%20turkeys.%20So%20the%20guests%20check%20in%20on%20Thanksgiving%20night%2C%20they%20prep%20the%20food%2C%20they're%20ready%20too%20cook%20for%20whole%20family%2C%20they%20open%20the%20oven%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20oven%20rack.%20On%20Thanksgiving%2C%20it's%20not%20easy%20to%20contact%20the%20manufacturer%20of%20the%20oven%20and%20find%20an%20oven%20rack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20just%20see%20crazy%20scenarios.%20Why%20would%20you%20even%20take%20an%20oven%20rack%3F%20We%20had%20an%20oven%20rack%20in%20that%20home%20for%2010%20or%2011%20months%20on%20Airbnb.%20And%20it%20just%20happened%20to%20be%20gone%20the%20one%20day%20you%20really%20need%20it.%20It's%20possible%20a%20previous%20guest%20broke%20it%2C%20didn't%20want%20us%20to%20see%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20catch%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%20a%20property%20owner%20who%20lived%20nearby%20happened%20to%20have%20the%20same%20exact%20oven%20model%20and%20was%20able%20to%20lend%20her%20oven%20rack.%20But%20now%2C%20checking%20for%20oven%20racks%20is%20part%20of%20the%20holiday%20checklist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20have%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20anything%20to%20go%20wrong%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20kind%20of%20funny%20in%20most%20of%20our%20markets%2C%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20Thanksgiving%2C%20and%20then%20the%20weeks%20in%20between%20Thanksgiving%20and%20Christmas%20are%20totally%20quiet.%20Then%20we%20get%20to%20the%20week%20of%20Thanksgiving%20and%20the%20week%20of%20Christmas%20and%20New%20Year's%2C%20and%20it's%20like%20all%20hell%20breaks%20loose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20we%20had%20a%20guest%20check%20out%20of%20a%20property%20in%20the%20Poconos%20and%20it%20looks%20like%20they%20had%20punched%20a%20hole%20through%20the%20glass%20in%20the%20front%20door.%20Our%20cleaner%20showed%20up%20to%20shattered%20glass%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20cold.%20It's%20November%20in%20Pennsylvania.%20And%20now%20there's%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20front%20door%20and%20a%20new%20reservation%20checking%20in%20in%20six%20hours.%20Also%20there's%20a%20bigger%20weight%20on%20us%20to%20get%20everything%20completely%20resolved%20because%20again%2C%20these%20are%20our%20highest%20payouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20property%20was%20a%20mountain%20town%20and%20it's%20not%20easy%20to%20get%20someone%20out%20there%20immediately.%20So%20many%20of%20the%20contractors%20we%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20said%20they%20already%20were%20taking%20breaks%20for%20Thanksgiving.%20We%20luckily%20got%20one%20of%20our%20team%20members%20who%20was%20able%20to%20get%20out%20there%20in%20time%20and%20patch%20it%20up%20pretty%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E