%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsafeway-stores-add-receipt-scanning-security-gates-to-self-checkout-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonitor%20the%20flow%20of%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20merchandise%20through%20a%20store.%20Sensormatic%20said%20its%20customers%20include%20Kroger%20but%20declined%20to%20share%20specifics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKroger%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESensormatic%20and%20others%20also%20offer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flowes-plans-stop-theft-power-tools-organized-crime-with-blockchain-system-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eradio-frequency%20identification%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20RFID%2C%20tagging.%20Items%20are%20marked%20with%20a%20unique%20code%20that%20can%20be%20detected%20by%20sensors%20throughout%20the%20store%2C%20allowing%20an%20item%20to%20be%20tracked%20from%20the%20shelf%20to%20the%20front%20door.%20The%20tags%20can%20also%20be%20automatically%20activated%20or%20deactivated%20as%20part%20of%20the%20self-checkout%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERFID%20tags%20are%20distinct%20from%20barcodes%2C%20which%20date%20back%20to%20the%20earliest%20self-checkout%20stations.%20Most%20point-of-sale%20systems%20still%20require%20scanning%20a%20label%2C%20even%20when%20cameras%20are%20monitoring%20the%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222194%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20overhead%20security%20camera%20at%20a%20Walmart%20self-checkout%20station.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654005ba356802a56be7d625%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221645%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20security%20camera%20keeps%20an%20overhead%20eye%20on%20each%20self-checkout%20station.%20%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20future%20free%20of%20barcodes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%