eral%20low-tech%20ways%20retailers%20have%20managed%20to%20curb%20shoplifting%20at%20self-checkout%20lanes.%20Other%20effective%20tools%20include%20using%20public-facing%20video%20monitors%2C%20giving%20front-end%20staff%20walkie-talkies%2C%20and%20simply%20installing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mashed.com%2F1163203%2Fself-checkout-reflection-altered-walmart-customers-brain-chemistry-in-2022%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emirror%20on%20the%20kiosk%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20low-tech%20strategies%20complement%20more%20expensive%20high-tech%20ones%20to%20reduce%20inventory%20losses.%20Sensormatic's%20Szklany%20said%20that%20even%20when%20unpaid%20merchandise%20does%20find%20its%20way%20out%20the%20door%2C%20these%20tools%20can%20help%20identify%20what%20kinds%20of%20products%20are%20stolen%20most%20often.%20Stores%20can%20then%20use%20that%20information%20to%20make%20targeted%20changes%20to%20displays%2C%20limit%20access%20to%20specific%20products%2C%20or%20build%20a%20case%20against%20a%20particular%20offender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretailers-using-tech-to-combat-theft-at-self-checkouts-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700736122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655cf8a222cf74a5739aedbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretailers-using-tech-to-combat-theft-at-self-checkouts-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Companies%20like%20Walmart%20and%20Kroger%20are%20outfitting%20their%20self-checkouts%20with%20cameras%2C%20AI-enabled%20sensors%2C%20and%20other%20tech.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dreuter%40insider.com%20(Dominick%20Reuter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretailers-using-tech-to-combat-theft-at-self-checkouts-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22amp