Wilders%E2%80%99%20party%E2%80%99s%20stunning%20election%20performance%20drew%20praise%20from%20nationalist%20and%20far-right%20European%20politicians.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20winds%20of%20change%20are%20here!%20Congratulations%20to%20Geert%20Wilders%20on%20winning%20the%20Dutch%20elections!%E2%80%9D%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fviktor-orban%2Ft-38337120%5C%22%3EHungarian%20Prime%20Minister%20Viktor%20Orban%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20far-right%20leader%20Marine%20Le%20Pen%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20Rassemblement%20National%20party%2C%20posted%20on%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CCongratulations%20to%20Geert%20Wilders%20and%20the%20PVV%20for%20their%20spectacular%20performance%20in%20the%20legislative%20elections%20which%20confirms%20the%20growing%20attachment%20to%20the%20defense%20of%20national%20identities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EItalian%20far-right%20leader%20and%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20Matteo%20Salvini%20also%20congratulated%20Wilders.%20%E2%80%9CCongratulations%20to%20our%20friend%20Geert%20Wilders%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20PVV%20and%20historic%20ally%20of%20the%20League%2C%20for%20this%20extraordinary%20electoral%20victory.%20A%20new%20Europe%20is%20possible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnxiety%20about%20the%20election%20results%20is%20growing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20also%20expressed%20trepidation%20over%20the%20election%20outcome.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Feu-climate-chief-we-need-to-be-more-ambitious%2Fa-59629194%5C%22%3EFrans%20Timmermans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20Green%2FLabor%20left-wing%20bloc%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CDemocracy%20has%20spoken%2C%20now%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20for%20us%20to%20defend%20democracy%2C%20to%20defend%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20We%20have%20to%20make%20a%20fist%20against%20exclusion%2C%20against%20discrimination.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20distress%20and%20fear%20are%20enormous%E2%80%A6%20Wilders%20is%2