paign.%20While%20media%20reports%20suggest%20that%20there%20is%20momentum%20for%20possible%20change%20of%20regime%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20by%20unseating%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20there%20is%20discernible%20trend%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20for%20the%20continuance%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20432px)%2085vw%2C%20432px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22432%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22356%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGehlot%E2%80%99s%20welfare%20schemes%20versus%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20promises%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20there%20is%20a%20neck-to-neck%20contest%20between%20Congress%20and%20BJP.%20The%20existing%20welfare%20schemes%20of%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20seven%20guarantees%20in%20its%20election%20manifesto%20%E2%80%93%20which%2C%20among%20others%20things%2C%20include%C2%A0%20Rs%2010%2C000%20every%20year%20to%20the%20female%20head%20of%20the%20family%20under%20the%20Griha%20Lakshmi%20Yojana%20guarantee%2C%20cow%20dung%20at%20Rs%202%20kg%20under%20the%20Gowdhan%20project%2C%20free%20laptops%20and%20tablets%20to%20first-year%20government%20college%20students%20%E2%80%93%20have%20gained%20traction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gehlot%20government%E2%80%99s%20scheme%20to%20give%20Rs%2025%20lakhs%20to%20people%20for%20medical%20treatment%20and%20its%20assurances%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%20(OPS)%20and%20providing%20free%20education%20has%20become%20very%20popular.%20In%20its%20manifesto%20released%20two%20days%20ago%2C%20four%20days%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20enhance%20the%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20promise%20to%20Rs%2050%20lakhs%20and%2C%20among%20other%20promises%2C%20assured%20that%20it%20will%20implement%20MSP%20for%20crops%20based%20on%20the%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20formula.%20It%20promises%20to%20give%20four%20lakh%20government%20jobs%2C%20and%2010%20lakh%20other%20jobs%2C%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20and%20give%20cooking%20gas%20cylinders%20to%20some%20families%20at%20Rs%20450%20per%20cylinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20promises%20to%20enact%20a%20legislation%20guaranteeing%20the%20right%20to%20shelter.%20In%20contrast%2C%20BJP%20in%20manifesto%20has%20assured%20gas%20cylinders%20for%20Rs%20500.%20Vey%20strikingly%2C%20it%20does%20not%20mention%20restoration%20of%20OPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECriticism%20of%20Gehlot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20regime%20was%20widely%20criticised%20by%20youth%20and%20people%20of%20the%20state%20on%20the%20paper%20leak%20issue%20which%20led%20to%20the%20cancellation%20of%20competitive%20exams%20for%20filling%20vacancies%20at%20government%20jobs.%20There%20is%20also%20anti-incumbency%20against%20Congress%20MLAs%20even%20though%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20personally%20enjoys%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20is%20defensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20several%20media%20commentators%20wonder%20how%20it%20is%20that%20in%20none%20of%20the%20BJP-ruled%20states%20gas%20cylinders%20are%20available%20for%20as%20cheap%20as%20Rs%20500.%20How%20can%20the%20party%20make%20such%20a%20promise%2C%20it%20asks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Modi%20Guarantees%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20fashioned%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20guarantees%20in%20Karnataka%20where%20it%20won%20a%20decisive%20mandate%20and%20BJP%20lost%20power.%20It%20is%20quite%20striking%20that%20while%20Congress%20calls%20those%20guarantees%20as%20those%20of%20the%20party%2C%20to%20the%20people%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP%20names%20the%20promises%20it%20has%20stated%20as%20%E2%80%98Modi%E2%80%99s%20Guarantees%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20BJP%20follows%20the%20Congress%20example%20of%20%C2%A0giving%20guarantees%20it%20centres%20these%20around%20Modi.%20The%20unmistakable%20centrality%20of%20Modi%20in%20the%20template%20of%20the%20BJP%20campaign%20in%20Rajasthan%20is%20projected%20before%20the%20electorate%20to%20appear%20as%20if%20Modi%20is%20the%20driving%20force%20for%20every%20thing%20associated%20with%20party%E2%80%99s%20quest%20for%20power%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20strategy%20is%20best%20manifested%20in%20an%20election%20rally%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20in%20Rajasthan%20which%20began%20from%20a%20Hanuman%20temple%20where%20there%20were%20bomb%20blasts%20some%20years%20ago%20and%20traversed%20through%20the%20area.%20Many%20wondered%20if%20the%20route%20would%20give%20birth%20to%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20beheading%20of%20a%20Hindu%20tailor%20Kanhiya%20Lal%20in%20Rajasthan%20last%20year%20by%20Muslims%20because%20of%20the%20alleged%20insult%20of%20Prophet%20Mohammad%20by%20a%20BJP%20spokesperson%20has%20been%20frequently%20invoked%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20to%20appeal%20to%20voters.%20One%20BJP%20leader%20went%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20saying%20that%20the%20victory%20of%20Congress%20will%20cause%20celebrations%20in%20Pakistan.%20Such%20statements%20might%20cause%20polarisation%20of%20voters%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDharma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20struggles%20in%20the%20state%20do%20not%20mean%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20assured%20of%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%2C%20apart%20from%20solely%20relying%20on%20local%20leaders%20and%20taking%20up%20local%20socio-economic%20issues%20is%20reaching%20out%20to%20voters%20through%20its%20guarantees%20and%20manifesto%2C%20which%20it%20claimed%20is%20based%20on%20the%20rights%20of%20people%2C%20regardless%20of%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedia%20personality%20Vijaya%20Vidrohi%20succinctly%20put%20the%20electoral%20contest%20of%20%E2%80%98Congress%20vs%20BJP%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20contest%20between%20%E2%80%98Raj%20Dharma%20vs%20Dharma%E2%80%99.%20While%20Raj%20Dharma%20represents%20the%20rule%20or%20governance%20for%20promoting%20welfare%20of%20people%20without%20any%20discrimination%20based%20on%20their%20identities%2C%20the%20Dharma%20here%20represents%20Hindutva%20strategy%20which%20does%20not%20include%20Muslims.%20He%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20eventually%20people%20might%20get%20persuaded%20more%20by%20Raj%20Dharma%20rather%20than%20mere%20Dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20quoted%20a%20famous%20line%20from%20the%20folklore%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ERub%20Ruthe%2C%20Raj%20Na%20Ruthe%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGod%20might%20be%20angry%2C%20but%20the%20King%20should%20not%20be%20angry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20regional%20leaders%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20under%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20has%20relegated%20regional%20leaders%20in%20almost%20all%20the%20states%20to%20secondary%20status%20and%20in%20Rajasthan%20it%20has%20been%20done%20to%20three-time%20chief%20minister%20and%20highly%20influential%20leader%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia.%20She%20was%20reportedly%20not%20given%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20party%20manifesto%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20release%20when%20she%20was%20there%20on%20the%20dais%20with%20BJP%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda.%20Eventually%20someone%20gave%20a%20copy%20to%20her%20and%20she%20stood%20with%20it%20in%20hand%2C%20without%20displaying%20it%20for%20media%20coverage.%20The%20visual%20message%20is%20clear.%20She%20is%20also%20not%20visiting%20constituencies%20other%20than%20her%20own%20for%20campaigns%20and%20on%20one%20occasion%20publicly%20declared%20that%20she%20would%20retire%20as%20her%20son%20is%20now%20able%20to%20take%20care%20of%20himself%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20marginalisation%20of%20a%20key%20regional%20leader%20like%20her%20in%20the%20electoral%20battle%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20overwhelming%20reliance%20of%20the%20party%20on%20Hindutva%20and%20Modi%20and%20not%20on%20its%20own%20manifesto%20leads%20one%20to%20wonder%20which%20brand%20of%20campaigns%20will%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20Served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700729008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23141227%2FUntitled-design-3-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-rajasthan-a-contest-between-dharma-and-raj-dharma%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20has%20marginalised%20key%20leaders.%20The%20Congress%20has%20focused%20on%20an%20ambitious%20manifesto.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-rajasthan-a-contest-between-dharma-and-raj-dharma%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20plans%20to%20ask%20ONGC%20to%20consider%20%241.9%20billion%20rights%20issue%20to%20fund%20HPCL%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700728624000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2019-12%2F20%2Ffull%2F1576864311-1607.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.b