re%20I%20assumed%20office%20on%20October%203%2C%202018.%20My%20transfer%20order%20seemed%20to%20have%20been%20issued%20with%20an%20ill%20intention%20to%20harass%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fchief-justice-pritinker-diwaker-transfer-allahabad-high-court-cji-dipak-misra-collegium-ill-intended%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20judge%20said%20on%20his%20last%20day%20in%20office%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%20explain%20what%20the%20ill%20intention%20or%20alleged%20harassment%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Diwaker%2C%20however%2C%20thanked%20the%20current%20CJI%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20under%20whose%20leadership%20the%20Collegium%20recommended%20him%20for%20the%20position%20of%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBorn%20in%201961%2C%20Justice%20Diwakar%20graduated%20in%20law%20from%20Durgawati%20University%20in%20Jabalpur%20and%20enrolled%20as%20an%20advocate%20in%201984.%20He%20was%20designated%20as%20a%20senior%20advocate%20in%20January%202005%20and%20elevated%20as%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20high%20court%20in%202009.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20farewell%20speech%2C%20Justice%20Diwakar%20said%20that%20his%20transfer%20to%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%2C%20although%20unwarranted%2C%20%E2%80%9Cturned%20into%20boon%20for%20me%20because%20I%20received%20immeasurable%20support%20and%20cooperation%20from%20my%20companion%20judges%20as%20well%20as%20from%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Bar.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20been%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20HC%20since%20October%203%2C%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20praised%20the%20Allahabad%20HC%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgreat%20institution%20which%20has%20its%20unique%20style%20of%20working%20and%20traditions%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20matter%20of%20pride%E2%80%9D%20for%20him%20to%20have%20worked%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBalancing%20a%20heavy%20workload%20is%20indeed%20a%20challenge%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court.%20Furthermore%2C%20this%20court%20was%20subjected%20to%20criticism%20from%20various%20corners%20in%20relation%20to%20its%20functioning.%20But%20I%20am%20of%20the%20firm%20belief%20that%20before%20reaching%20a%20particular%20conclusion%2C%20critics%20must%20see%20the%20difficulties%20and%20shortcomings%20prevailing%20in%20the%20institution%20from%20the%20inside%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20retiring%20judge%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20came%20at%20his%20farewell%20function%20in%20Prayagraj%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Justice%20Bibek%20Chaudhuri%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20transferred%20from%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20to%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%2C%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Collegium.%20%E2%80%9CI%20must%20say%20that%20in%201975%20during%20Emergency%2C%2016%20judges%20of%20different%20High%20Courts%20were%20transferred%20by%20an%20executive%20decision%20in%20one%20go.%20After%20almost%2048%20years%2C%2024%20judges%20have%20been%20transferred%20from%20one%20High%20Court%20to%20another%20by%20the%20Collegium%20of%20the%20Honorable%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20one%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Chaudhuri%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcalcutta-high-court-justice-bibek-chaudhuri-emergency-judiciary-executive%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20farewell%20speech%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Chaudhuri%20said%20that%20his%20transfer%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20beginning%20of%20the%20introduction%20and%20implementation%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%201983%20policy%20that%20the%20chief%20justices%20of%20high%20courts%20and%20one-third%20of%20the%20high%2