0over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20death%20of%20Group%20founder%20Subrata%20Roy%20on%20November%2014%2C%20there%20is%20a%20heightened%20sense%20of%20insecurity%20and%20urgency%20on%20the%20part%20of%20investors%20who%20are%20spread%20across%2027%20states%20across%20the%20country.%20With%20the%20portal%20launched%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20July%20to%20facilitate%20the%20refunds%20yet%20to%20take%20off%20and%20the%20allegations%20against%20authorities%20that%20claims%20are%20being%20rejected%20on%20%E2%80%9Cfrivolous%20grounds%E2%80%9D%2C%20there%20is%20consternation%20among%20lakhs%20of%20investors%20who%20fear%20that%20their%20money%20would%20be%20transferred%20to%20Consolidated%20Fund%20of%20India%20in%20the%20name%20of%20unclaimed%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhay%20Dev%20Shukla%2C%20president%20of%20a%20registered%20body%20representing%20the%20Sahara%20investors%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fabout-five-lakh-sahara-group-investors-to-protest-in-delhi-against-governments-failure-to-refund-their-deposits%2Farticle67562508.ece%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20if%20the%20government%20confiscated%20the%20Sahara%20chairperson%E2%80%99s%20property%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20money%20of%20crores%20of%20investors%20will%20be%20lost%2C%20which%20cannot%20be%20tolerated%20at%20any%20cost%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20December%2C%20depositors%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20will%20reach%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Jantar%20Mantar%20and%20will%20%3Ci%3Egherao%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E(surround)%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20Central%20Registrar%20of%20Cooperative%20Societies%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shukla%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20on%20July%2018%20launched%20the%20Central%20Registrar%20of%20Cooperative%20Societies%20(CRCS)%20portal%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmocrefund.crcs.gov.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Emocrefund.crcs.gov.in%3C%2Fa%3E)%20for%20small%20investors%20in%20four%20cooperatives%20%E2%80%94%20Sahara%20Credit%20Cooperative%20Society%20Limited%2C%20Saharayn%20Universal%20Multipurpose%20Society%20Limited%2C%20Humara%20India%20Credit%20Cooperative%20Society%20Limited%2C%20and%20Stars%20Multipurpose%20Cooperative%20Society%20Limited.%20These%20were%20registered%20from%20March%202010%20to%20January%202014%2C%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20Bhopal%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20and%20Kolkata%2C%20respectively%2C%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Multi-State%20Cooperative%20Societies%20Act%2C%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20the%20real%20intention%20behind%20such%20a%20portal%20is%20to%20give%20Roy%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsahara-chairmans-death-worries-small-time-investors-who-say-their-refund-claims-are-being-rejected-on-a-government-portal%2Farticle67544550.ece%5C%22%3Ean%20escape%20route%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20from%20multiple%20legal%20cases%20against%20him.%20He%20had%20questioned%20the%20rationale%20behind%20capping%20the%20refunds%20at%20Rs%2010%2C000%20irrespective%20of%20the%20value%20of%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CExcept%20his%20(Roy%E2%80%99s)%20wife%2C%20none%20of%20the%20family%20members%20are%20in%20India.%20How%20will%20we%20get%20our%20money%20back%3F%20The%20portal%20launched%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20was%20only%20to%20mislead%20the%20people.%2099.99%25%20of%20investors%20have%20not%20got%20their%20money%20back.%20Claims%20are%20being%20rejected%20on%20frivolous%20grounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsahara-chairmans-death-worries-small-time-investors-who-say-their-refund-claims-are-being-rejected-on-a-government-portal%2Farticle67544550.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20alleged%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Shukla%2C%20there%20are%2085%20lakh%20depositors%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%2055%20lakh%20depositors%20in%20Bihar%2C%204%20lakh%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%2018%20lakh%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%2020%20lakh%20in%20Odisha%2C%2014%20lakh%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20eight%20lakh%20each%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Assam%2C%20six%20lakh%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20five%20lakh%20each%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Delhi%2C%20four%20lakh%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20three%20lakh%20each%20in%20Telangana%20and%20Maharashtra.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20alone%2C%20he%20said%20there%20are%20about%C2%A01.5%20crore%20Sahara%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcrcs-sahara-refund-portal-to-help-crores-of-sahara-depositors-get-refund-amit-shah%2Farticle67093415.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20promised%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%2C%20during%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20portal%2C%20that%201.7%20crore%20investors%20would%20benefit%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20and%20claims%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20would%20be%20settled%20first.%20The%20money%20would%20be%20returned%20to%20the%20Aadhaar-linked%20bank%20accounts%20of%20the%20investors%20within%2045%20days%2C%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700719256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23112512%2FThe-Wire-86.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffive-lakh-sahara-group-investors-to-stage-protest-against-centre-in-delhi-for-refunds%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abhay%20Dev%20Shukla%2C%20president%20of%20a%20registered%20body%20representing%20the%20Sahara%20investors%2C%20said%20depositors%20from%20across%20the%20country%20will%20reach%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Jantar%20Mantar%20in%20December%20to%20'gherao%C2%A0(surround)'%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20Central%20Registrar%20of%20Cooperative%20Societies%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20Prime%20Ministe