ri%20started%20on%20Sunday%2C%20November%2019%2C%20following%20repeated%20sightings%20of%20militants%20in%20the%20hilly%20district%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20was%20launched%20following%20an%20encounter%20in%20Rajouri%E2%80%99s%20Budhal%20on%20Friday%2C%20November%2017%2C%20in%20which%20a%20militant%20was%20killed.%20After%20this%20encounter%2C%20at%20least%20two%20tip-offs%20to%20security%20forces%20indicated%20that%20militants%20were%20seeking%20food%20from%20locals%20in%20some%20residential%20areas%20of%20Rajouri%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20a%20joint%20team%20of%20security%20forces%20comprising%20the%20Army%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20among%20other%20central%20paramilitary%20forces%20launched%20a%20search%20operation%20in%20a%20forested%20area%20of%20Gulabgarh%20in%20Kalakote%20tehsil%20of%20Rajouri%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20mopping%20operation%20entered%20its%20fourth%20day%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20the%20joint%20team%20came%20under%20intense%20fire%20by%20a%20group%20of%20two%20to%20three%20heavily%20armed%20militants%20in%20Baajimal%20area.%20Sources%20said%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20fire%20was%20so%20high%20that%20the%20joint%20team%20had%20to%20retreat%2C%20leaving%20some%20of%20the%20injured%20behind%2C%20and%20regroup%2C%20before%20taking%20on%20the%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Peoples%20Anti-Fascist%20Force%20(PAFF)%20which%20the%20officials%20believe%20is%20an%20offshoot%20of%20the%20banned%2C%20Pakistan-based%20terror%20outfit%2C%20Jaish-e-Mohammad%2C%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack%2C%20according%20to%20open%20source%20intelligence%20posts%20on%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0couldn%E2%80%99t%20immediately%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20these%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deadly%20shootout%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fkokernag-operation-anantnag-fourth-soldier-killed%5C%22%3Ebears%20resemblance%20to%20a%20similar%20attack%20on%20security%20forces%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kokernag%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%20in%20which%20the%20Army%20lost%20a%20Commanding%20Officer%20and%20a%20Major%20among%20four%20soldiers%20while%20an%20injured%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20awaiting%20rescue%2C%20bled%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Kokernag%20operation%2C%20security%20forces%20were%20following%20a%20tip-off%20about%20the%20presence%20of%20militants%20in%20the%20mountainous%20Gadool%20village%20which%20led%20them%20into%20an%20ambush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-risk%20operation%2C%20in%20which%20militants%20are%20known%20to%20leverage%20the%20heights%20of%20mountains%20and%20dense%20vegetation%20to%20their%20strategic%20advantage%2C%20turned%20into%20one%20of%20the%20deadliest%20attacks%20on%20security%20forces%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strategic%20advantages%20of%20height%20and%20thick%20forest%20cover%20had%20stretched%20the%20encounter%20in%20Gadool%20to%20six%20days%20as%20security%20forces%20proceeded%20cautiously%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20more%20casualties%20in%20their%20ranks%20while%20closing%20in%20around%20the%20perpetrators%20who%20were%20hiding%20on%20a%20mountainside%20with%20natural%2C%20cave-like%20structures%20beneath%20a%20canopy%20of%20dense%20vegetation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20PAFF%20militants%20deliberately%20showed%20up%20in%20residential%20areas%20of%20Rajouri%20recently%20to%20bait%20the%20security%20forces%20and%20draw%20them%20out%20on%20a%20manhunt%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20the%20hilly%20district%20without%20assessing%20the%20risks%20remains%20a%20matter%20of%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20shot%20near%20the%20site%20of%20the%20shootout%2C%20which%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20shows%20two%20men%20in%20civvies%20accompanying%20a%20team%20of%20Army%20soldiers%20who%20are%20hauling%20a%20cot%20down%20a%20hillock%20on%20their%20shoulders.%20An%20unidentified%20body%2C%20purportedly%20one%20of%20the%20Army%20soldiers%20killed%20in%20the%20shootout%2C%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20video%20laying%20motionless%20on%20the%20cot%20under%20a%20red%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20immediately%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20slain%20soldiers%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Captain%20MV%20Pranjal%20of%2063%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20and%20Captain%20Shubham%20Gupta%20and%20Havildar%20Majid%20Ahmad%2C%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20elite%209%20PARA%20unit.%20The%20identity%20of%20the%20fourth%20soldier%20was%20not%20immediately%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Army%20major%20and%20another%20soldier%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20shootout%20but%20their%20condition%20is%20reportedly%20stable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%20the%20bodies%20of%20Captain%20Gupta%20and%20Havildar%20Majid%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Poonch%2C%20have%20been%20recovered.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20continuous%20firing%20by%20the%20heavily-armed%20militants%2C%20the%20bodies%20of%20Captain%20Pranjal%20and%20the%20unidentified%20soldier%20have%20not%20been%20retrieved%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPir%20Panjal%20a%20militancy%20epicentre%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20bifurcation%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20into%20two%20Union%20territories%2C%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%2C%20which%20comprises%20twin%20districts%20of%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%2C%20and%20parts%20of%20Reasi%20district%2C%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20new%20epicentre%20of%20militancy%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20militancy-related%20violence%20and%20local%20recruitment%20has%20gone%20down%20significantly%20in%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20the%20focus%20of%20violence%20has%20seemingly%20shifted%20to%20Jammu%20which%20was%20a%20militancy-free%20region%20before%20August%205%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20deadliest%20attacks%20on%20security%20forces%20and%20civilians%20have%20been%20reported%20from%20Rajouri%20since%202019.%20Five%20soldiers%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20Special%20Forces%20unit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fjammu%2Fencounter-underway-in-jks-rajouri-district-8592648%2F%5C%22%3Ewere%20killed%20in%20an%20ambush%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Budhal%20area%20of%20Rajouri%20while%20an%20officer%20was%20injured%20in%20an%20IED%20explosion%20in%20May%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20civilians%20including%20two%20children%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmilitants-shoot-dead-civilians-in-rajouri%2Farticle66327745.ece%5C%22%3Ewere%20killed%20on%20the%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20eve%20this%20year%20in%20Dhangri%20area%20of%20Rajouri%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202022%2C%20five%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20predawn%20suicide%20attack%20on%20an%20Army%20camp%20in%20Rajouri%E2%80%99s%20Darhal%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20an%20unspecified%20number%20of%20highly%20trained%20militants%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20foreigners%2C%20have%20taken%20refuge%20in%20the%20upper%20reaches%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20where%20they%20plan%20terror%20attacks%20on%20civilians%20and%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20agencies%20believe%20that%20some%20locals%20in%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20provide%20logistical%20support%20to%20these%20foreigners%20by%20using%20mobile%20phones%20that%20run%20on%20the%20SIM%20cards%20of%20Pakistan-based%20telecom%20operators.%20The%20signal%20of%20some%20of%20these%20operators%20spills%20over%20into%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20has%20also%20blamed%20Pakistan%20for%20supplying%20arms%2C%20ammunition%2C%20cash%20and%20drugs%20through%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20using%20human%20resources%20and%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20Jammu-based%2016%20Corps%20said%20on%20X%20that%20a%20joint%20team%20of%20security%20forces%20established%20contact%20with%20the%20militants%20in%20Rajouri%20on%20Thursday%20morning%20and%20an%20intense%20firefight%20broke%20out%20in%20which%20an%20unspecified%20number%20of%20terrorists%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COperations%20are%20in%20progress%2C%20amidst%20acts%20of%20valour%20and%20sacrifice%20by%20own%20bravehearts%20in%20trying%20to%20prevent%20collateral%20damage%20to%20women%20and%20children%20in%20the%20highest%20traditions%20of%C2%A0%23IndianArmy.%C2%A0%23Whiteknightcorps%C2%A0salutes%20the%20supreme%20sacrifice%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Army%20spokesperson%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700709351000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23084842%2F8797984514_f4c7161352_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fjammu-kashmir-militant-rajouri-encounter-four-soldiers-army-killed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20operation%20was%20launched%20following%20an%20encounter%20in%20Rajouri%E2%80%99s%20Budhal%20on%20November%2017%2C%20in%20which%20a%20militant%20was%20killed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fjammu-kashmir-militant-rajouri-encounter-four-soldiers-army-killed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Last%20Film%20Show%E2%80%99%20Director%20Pan%20Nalin%20Boards%20Himalayas-Set%20Debut%20Feature%20%E2%80%98Second%20Chance%E2%80%99%20as%20Executive%20Producer%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700708485000%2C%22visual%22%