st%20systems%20in%20place.%20For%20example%2C%20Erode%20district%20in%20the%20state%20is%20well%20developed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20remote%20pockets%20like%20Kathirimalai%2C%20which%20are%20located%20deep%20within%20the%20forest%2C%20are%20inaccessible%20given%20its%20geographically%20difficult%20terrain.%20Tribal%20residents%20have%20to%20trek%20for%203-4%20hours%20one%20way%20to%20avail%20health%20services.%20This%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20avail%20of%20any%20other%20welfare%20services%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-1-1700489624.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kathirimalai%20has%20been%20connected%20with%20a%205GHz%20Wi-Fi%20network%20to%20provide%20tele-medicine%20and%20tele-education%20services%20to%20tribal%20residents.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-1-1700489624.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-1-1700489624-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-1-1700489624-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-1-1700489624-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-1-1700489624-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334539%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKathirimalai%20has%20been%20connected%20with%20a%205GHz%20Wi-Fi%20network%20to%20provide%20telemedicine%20and%20tele-education%20services%20to%20tribal%20residents.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20trekkin