%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F36520866_260167804620539_7553707872811483136_o-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334475%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Preparing%20for%20UPSC%20CSE%20but%20struggling%20with%20motivation%3F%20The%20stories%20of%20these%205%20inspiring%20IAS%20officers%20will%20remind%20you%20of%20the%20power%20of%20perseverance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A80%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334475%2Finspiring-ias-officers-who-cracked-upsc-cse%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Bayer%20Is%20Delivering%20Medical%20Care%20at%20the%20Doorsteps%20of%20Rural%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Bayer%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20rural%20healthcare%20system%20is%20strained%20due%20to%20a%20severe%20shortage%20of%20doctors%20and%20infrastructure.%20The%20Government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhmis.mohfw.gov.in%2Fdownloadfile%3Ffilepath%3Dpublications%2FRural-Health-Statistics%2FRHS%25202021-22.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ERural%20Health%20Statistics%202021-2022%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reveals%20a%20deficit%20of%2079.5%20percent%20in%20rural%20healthcare%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrimary%20Health%20Centres%20(PHC)%2C%20the%20initial%20point%20of%20care%20for%20villages%2C%20cater%20to%20around%2036%2C000%20people%20per%20PHC%2C%20as%20per%20the%20same%20report.%20PHCs%20typically%20have%20one%20medical%20officer%20who%20is%20a%20physician%2C%20staff%20nurses%2C%20and%20Auxiliary%20Nurses%20and%20Midwives%20(ANM)%20along%20with%20other%20staff%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInadequate%20infrastructure%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316087%2Fassam-couple-helps-rural-northeast-india-access-affordable-mental-healthcare-mita%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20patient%20load%3C%2Fa%3E%20contribute%20to%20significant%20stress%20on%20doctors%20and%20nurses.%20Villagers%20have%20to%20travel%20for%20about%2045%20minutes%20to%20reach%20the%20nearest%20district%20hospital%20to%20access%20a%20specialist.%20To%20address%20these%20issues%2C%20Bayer%20Foundation%20India%20(BFI)%20has%20established%20telemedicine%20centres%20at%20PHCs%20to%20bring%20top%20healthcare%20professionals%20to%20local%20communities%2C%20right%20at%20their%20doorstep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarita%20Bahl%20%E2%80%94%20Country%20Group%20CSR%20Head%2C%20Bayer%2C%20South%20Asia%20%26amp%3B%20Director%2C%20Bayer%20Foundation%20India%20%E2%80%94%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20travelled%20to%20many%20districts%20across%20the%20country%20like%20Raichur%2C%20Khandwa%2C%20and%20Tikamgarh%2C%20and%20saw%20that%20there%20was%20very%20little%20support%20available%20in%20PHCs.%20People%20have%20to%20travel%20several%20kilometres%20just%20to%20see%20a%20specialist%2C%20and%20many%20may%20not%20go.%20So%20we%20realised%20that%20rather%20than%20building%20something%20new%2C%20we%20should%20make%20healthcare%20better%2C%20affordable%20and%20accessible%20right%20at%20the%20PHC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Bayer%20has%20set%20up%2028%20%E2%80%98Phygital%E2%80%99%20telemedicine%20centres%20in%2014%20aspirational%20districts%20(a%20programme%20by%20the%20government%20to%20improve%20underdeveloped%20districts%20nationwide)%20across%20eight%20states%2C%20Sarita%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStrengthening%20the%20health%20index%20of%20the%20rural%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2